title: 6.9 Gave the Tentacle Monster More Ways to Penetrate Magic Resist
body:
The patch with one of the most memeful numbers gives a character who is commonly associated with [redacted] more true damage, which ignores/penetrates resistances.

Is Riot trying to tell us something?  Was this intentional or pure coincidence?  IS VEL'KOZ TRULY ENGROSSED WITH ANAL?!  WILL I EVER STOP ASKING QUESTIONS THAT WON'T BE ANSWERED?!
